thread.title_full: TackleDirect reviewed by Michael K. - Chicago, IL

author: Michael K. - Chicago, IL
title: Michael K. - Chicago, IL
text: I recently purchased a new St. Croix rod from TackleDirect. The ordering process was clear and simple. The rod arrived very well packaged in a strong, secured tube and in a very timely manner. I'll be doing more business with TackleDirect.
